name: Fish Stick: On it's way to hell
name_original: Fish Stick: On it's way to hell
description:
Fish Stick: On it's way to hell

This game is about the terrible life of a fish, which almost becomes a fried fish stick.
You got caught by a boat and now people want to fry you in a pan!
Don't get hit by the knife to stay alive!

Have fun!

WouterK12

(this game was made in 19 hours, for Dani's Basement Jam #2)
